       오늘의 메뉴는 아직 동지는 아니지만 미리 만들어본 동지팥죽 만들기 레시피를 올려 드렸어요.   아마도 준비를 하시는 분들도 있을 테고 평상시에도 쑤어서 드시는 분들도 계실 텐데 이번에는   사서 먹지 말고 직접 만들어서 내 가족들과 함께 맛있게 드셔 보시는 건 어떠세요.   식혀 먹어도 맛나지만 저는 따뜻할 때 한 그릇 먹었답니다.                   ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  ","images":["http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141203_122/real5030_1417579479483biBcz_JPEG/IMG_9426.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141203_298/real5030_1417579479689o0gcS_JPEG/IMG_9399.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141203_155/real5030_1417579532316vgufS_JPEG/45.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141203_297/real5030_1417579605530EK8QF_JPEG/566.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141203_205/real5030_1417579626761N2ms7_JPEG/5.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141203_216/real5030_1417579785341Q27nD_JPEG/67.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141203_177/real5030_1417579680011x4ssp_JPEG/78.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141203_102/real5030_1417579660235gyi8x_JPEG/6776.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb3.phinf.naver.net/20141203_30/real5030_1417579741332f6jrC_JPEG/6756554.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141203_29/real5030_1417579741621eQkWN_JPEG/65743.jpg?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141203_29/real5030_1417579872489OBP2D_JPEG/IMG_9424.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb4.phinf.naver.net/20141203_187/real5030_1417579872636OBtax_JPEG/IMG_9428.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141203_281/real5030_1417579911907EUGxx_JPEG/IMG_9431.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141203_168/real5030_1417579912058X1xd2_JPEG/IMG_9429.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141203_113/real5030_1417579912208YuEwq_JPEG/IMG_9432.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb2.phinf.naver.net/20141203_241/real5030_1417579912353ArVtH_JPEG/IMG_9430.JPG?type=","http://mblogthumb1.phinf.naver.net/20141203_224/real5030_1417579912567K82TG_JPEG/IMG_9